  "title": "P3-P6 English teacher (Full time/Part time)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>-         Deliver dynamic, clear, and engaging lessons based on lesson plans.</p>\n<p>-         Develop lesson plans and resources to support students’ academic success.</p>\n<p>-         Build strong relationships with both students and parents.</p>\n<p>-         Provide timely feedback to help students reach their full potential.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>-         At least a bachelor’s degree or equivalent.</p>\n<p>-         Up to date with latest MOE syllabus.</p>\n<p>-         Able to customize teaching materials for different learning levels.</p>\n<p>-         A dynamic and approachable personality.</p>\n<p>-         Strong communication and teamwork skills.</p>\n<p>-         Passion for teaching and helping students succeed.</p>\n<p>-         Candidate must be able to work on weekdays evenings, weekends.</p>\n<p>-         Candidate with teaching experience will be advantageous.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p>1. AWS + Performance bonus.</p>\n<p>2. Enjoys insurance and medical subsidy, annual leaves, medical leaves.</p>\n<p>3. Flexible working culture.</p>\n<p>4. Career growth opportunities &amp; Staff incentive.</p>\n<p>5. Part time teachers will depend on past experience.</p>\n<p>6. Children of the Company's full-time teachers are eligible for a waiver of tuition fees.</p>\n<p><strong>Working hour</strong></p>\n<p>5.5 days/44 hours per week.</p>\n<p>Any interested please:</p>\n<p>Email: admin@unitimes.sg Or WhatsApp: +65 97591599 (Ms Jessy)</p>",
